{"tid":1794750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［民間記者會］逆權運動現生機   素人工會抗強權","createTime":"2019-12-23T10:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:28:30.000Z","uid":325953,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"9679e730852a5b30771701a8ab627b3681ab3fd9","tid":1794750,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5HiDjZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5HiDjZ.jpg&h=228b73fc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">逆權運動現生機  <br />\n素人工會抗強權</div></span><br />\n<br />\n組織工會除了保障打工仔權益，對抗爭運動亦有深遠影響。民間記者會邀請了數個正積極籌備工會的代表嘉賓，分享現時成立工會的進展，招募會員的情況並簡述有關工會的方向和計劃。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年12月23日（星期一）<br />\n時間：晚上7:00🕖<br />\n<br />\n📍大家可於以下或其他頻道收看直播：<br />\n基進報導：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c5ed2113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/</a> <br />\n反送中直播：<a href=\"http://www.hklivegroup.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklivegroup.com%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=1eb9a0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklivegroup.com/</a> （首次觀睇需要下載加密插件）<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=5f67a554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/</a><br />\n香港蘋果日報：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=40852391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com